description: BTC Domination was one of the most engaging projects in our entire ecosystem! We asked the community to help us hunt Inscription #1000000. During that epic adventure, the community inscribed thousands of BTC logos by themselves, trying to catch the inscription. An opportunity for all to learn about inscriptions and transaction fees, but also, proving how strong the BTC Machine community really is! For many, this was their first ordinal, and they inscribed it themselves!
name: BTC Domination
